\]
\[
(0.7)^8 = 0.05764801
\]
\[
P(N=8) = 0.05764801
\]
\[
P(N \geq 7) = 0.19765032 + 0.05764801 = 0.25529833
\]
Rounding 0.25529833 to three decimal places gives 0.255, as the fourth decimal digit (2) is less than 5.

